{
  "texts": [
    "The types of interaction are separated by their DoF, so Head Movement and Point and Click are exclusive to 3DoF and Teleport Locomotion, Gamepad Locomotion, and Room Scale are exclusive to 6DoF.",
    "On the one hand, it can be observed that the 3DoF standalone is the most popular HMD in 3DoF experiences, followed by 6DoF 360º external tracking desktop HMDs.",
    "Furthermore, the latter HMD was only used for experiences with a Head Movement system.",
    "On the other hand, 6DoF experiences showed more differences.",
    "Reviewing the types of HMD, the most widely used were in general also used in 6DoF experiences, in the following order: 6DoF 360°external trackers desktop HMDs, 6DoF 180º external tracking desktop HMDs, and finally Fig. 16 Usage rates of different types of interaction in relation to type of iVR and DoF 6DoF internal tracking desktop and standalone HMDs."
  ]
}